title: Search & Filtering
---

## Overview

Allow users to quickly find customers and feedback.

## Requirements

- Text search on name/email/phone/message (indexed fields).
- Faceted filters: status, tags, channel, date range.
- Pagination and sort; preserve query in URL.

### API samples

```http
GET /v1/customers?search=smith&tags=vip&take=20&cursor=...
```

```http
GET /v1/feedback?status=SUBMITTED&channel=email&from=2025-01-01&to=2025-01-31
```

